<font color="yellow">Ayo kita ke rumah sakit.</font>

375
00:23:20,149 --> 00:23:22,379
<font color="yellow">Kau tak lihat dia terluka parah?
Aku harus cepat memperbaikinya?</font>

376
00:23:22,379 --> 00:23:24,719
<font color="yellow">Itu tidak penting.
Bagaimana denganmu?</font>

377
00:23:24,719 --> 00:23:26,549
<font color="yellow">Kau itu juga terluka!</font>

378
00:23:31,189 --> 00:23:32,430
<font color="yellow">Sadarlah.</font>

379
00:23:32,890 --> 00:23:35,000
<font color="yellow">Borg Mon hanyalah robot.</font>

380
00:23:39,600 --> 00:23:40,770
<font color="yellow">Dengarkan aku.</font>

381
00:23:41,640 --> 00:23:43,770
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak peduli
dia itu robot atau alien.</font>

382
00:23:43,770 --> 00:23:46,169
<font color="yellow">Aku hanya akan mengikuti kata hatiku saja.</font>

383
00:23:46,169 --> 00:23:47,410
<font color="yellow">Jadi aku pasti tahu.</font>

384
00:23:50,850 --> 00:23:53,379
<font color="yellow">Hyung, kau itu benar-benar gila.</font>

385
00:23:54,919 --> 00:23:56,350
<font color="yellow">Sebenarnya kau kenapa?</font>

386
00:24:01,719 --> 00:24:02,819
<font color="yellow">Kau tahu?</font>

387
00:24:05,430 --> 00:24:07,930
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana rasanya sendirian di sini...</font>

388
00:24:07,930 --> 00:24:10,129
<font color="yellow">...setelah melepaskan seseorang
yang kau cintai tanpa henti?</font>

389
00:24:14,239 --> 00:24:15,339
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak akan...</font>

390
00:24:16,469 --> 00:24:17,569
<font color="yellow">...membiarkannya siapa saja...</font>

391
00:24:18,609 --> 00:24:20,410
<font color="yellow">...pergi dari dunia ini lagi.</font>

392
00:24:37,730 --> 00:24:39,189
<font color="yellow">Sampai kau memperbaiki Borg Mom....</font>

393
00:24:40,799 --> 00:24:43,100
<font color="yellow">...aku akan mengurus Yool.</font>

394
00:24:47,370 --> 00:24:48,739
<font color="yellow">Taruh salep ke lukamu.</font>

395
00:24:48,939 --> 00:24:50,500
<font color="yellow">Kau itu kelihatan jelek.</font>

396
00:24:50,839 --> 00:24:51,969
<font color="yellow">Nanti kau bertambah jelek.</font>

397
00:24:58,710 --> 00:24:59,850
<font color="yellow">Hyung, kau...</font>

398
00:25:01,649 --> 00:25:02,850
<font color="yellow">...benar-benar gila.</font>

399
00:25:35,419 --> 00:25:36,580
<font color="yellow">(Kesedihan: 100 persen)</font>

400
00:25:36,580 --> 00:25:39,350
<font color="yellow">(Analisis selesai!)</font>

401
00:25:42,219 --> 00:25:43,219
<font color="yellow">Tubuhku...</font>

402
00:25:44,460 --> 00:25:46,390
<font color="yellow">...terasa aneh</font>

403
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:50,899
<font color="yellow">Kita harus pergi ke Maladewa...</font>

404
00:25:51,870 --> 00:25:53,129
<font color="yellow">...untuk mengambil segelas mojito.</font>

405
00:25:55,700 --> 00:25:56,899
<font color="yellow">Aku...</font>

406
00:25:57,569 --> 00:26:00,239
<font color="yellow">...sekarang
tidak bercanda.</font>

407
00:26:09,219 --> 00:26:11,489
<font color="yellow">Kau akan membuangku...</font>

408
00:26:13,390 --> 00:26:14,790
<font color="yellow">...saat aku rusak begini?</font>

409
00:26:15,719 --> 00:26:16,759
<font color="yellow">Bukan?</font>

410
00:26:17,390 --> 00:26:18,430
<font color="yellow">Apa?</font>

411
00:26:21,500 --> 00:26:22,500
<font color="yellow">Tidak.</font>

412
00:26:40,080 --> 00:26:41,879
<font color="yellow">Tidak, Borg Mom.</font>

413
00:26:48,719 --> 00:26:50,290
<font color="yellow">Ibunya Yool...</font>

414
00:26:50,759 --> 00:26:51,930
<font color="yellow">...istriku...,</font>

415
00:26:52,629 --> 00:26:53,930
<font color="yellow">...aku tidak mau kehilangan dia lagi.</font>

416
00:28:12,410 --> 00:28:14,680
<font color="yellow">(Pagi setelah 3 hari)</font>

417
00:28:41,870 --> 00:28:42,870
<font color="yellow">Ini.</font>

418
00:28:51,879 --> 00:28:54,250
<font color="yellow">Ibu, tapi kenapa kita
berangkat begitu pagi?</font>

419
00:28:54,549 --> 00:28:57,489
<font color="yellow">Apa? Ibu hanya tidak ingin
bertemu dengan seseorang.</font>

420
00:28:57,890 --> 00:28:59,850
<font color="yellow">Maksudnya paman Borg?</font>

421
00:29:02,089 --> 00:29:03,089
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana kau...</font>

422
00:29:05,089 --> 00:29:08,200
<font color="yellow">Tidak.</font>

423
00:29:08,200 --> 00:29:12,069
<font color="yellow">Bohong. Aku tahu sesuatu
karena kalian begitu dekat.</font>

424
00:29:13,270 --> 00:29:15,469
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana kalau langsung membilas mulut?</font>

425
00:29:20,710 --> 00:29:23,439
<font color="yellow">Dasar.
Benar kau ini putriku.</font>

426
00:29:23,640 --> 00:29:25,480
<font color="yellow">Ah, rasanya sangat menyegarkan.</font>

427
00:29:31,250 --> 00:29:33,589
<font color="yellow">Akhir-akhir ini selalu berisik.
Apa yang terjadi?</font>

428
00:29:33,589 --> 00:29:36,890
<font color="yellow">Ibu, suara itu berasal
dari rumah Borg?</font>

429
00:29:37,290 --> 00:29:38,660
<font color="yellow">Dari kedengarannya...,</font>

430
00:29:38,859 --> 00:29:40,660
<font color="yellow">...suaranya seperti sedang
merusak perabotan.</font>

431
00:29:40,660 --> 00:29:42,060
<font color="yellow">Tapi ini sangat aneh.</font>

432
00:29:42,330 --> 00:29:44,669
<font color="yellow">Orang tua Borg sekarang sedang jalan-jalan.</font>

433
00:29:44,730 --> 00:29:46,930
<font color="yellow">Jadi Yool menginap
di rumah pamannya.</font>

434
00:29:47,100 --> 00:29:49,700
<font color="yellow">Katanya rumahnya sedang kosong.</font>

435
00:29:50,710 --> 00:29:52,540
<font color="yellow">Ibu, bagaimana kalau...</font>

436
00:29:52,540 --> 00:29:54,480
<font color="yellow">...ada dokkaebi di rumah Borg?</font>

437
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:56,080
<font color="yellow">Aku takut!</font>

438
00:29:56,980 --> 00:29:58,509
<font color="yellow">Semuanya baik-baik saja.</font>

439
00:29:58,980 --> 00:30:02,549
<font color="yellow">Orang tua terkadang bertengkar hebat tapi
tidak pernah memberi tahu anak mereka tentang itu.</font>

440
00:30:02,719 --> 00:30:04,620
<font color="yellow">- Apa?
- Apa?</font>

441
00:30:05,450 --> 00:30:06,520
<font color="yellow">Lupakan!</font>

442
00:30:06,520 --> 00:30:10,259
<font color="yellow">Aigoo, putri cantikku.
Kita harus cepat-cepat.</font>

443
00:30:10,259 --> 00:30:11,430
<font color="yellow">Berikan pada Ibu.</font>

444
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:21,200
<font color="yellow">Oke.</font>

445
00:30:29,939 --> 00:30:31,450
<font color="yellow">Paman Young Cheol.</font>

446
00:30:31,450 --> 00:30:34,549
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau
menjemputku secepat ini?</font>

447
00:30:34,549 --> 00:30:35,549
<font color="yellow">Apa?</font>

448
00:30:37,020 --> 00:30:39,319
<font color="yellow">Oh, kudengar ada yang datang lebih awal.</font>

449
00:30:40,859 --> 00:30:42,790
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana?
Aku terlihat tampan?</font>

450
00:30:42,790 --> 00:30:46,790
<font color="yellow">Paman, kau sudah menanyaiku
begitu sebanyak seratus sekali.</font>

451
00:30:47,759 --> 00:30:51,069
<font color="yellow">Tapi suasanamu bagus
walau kau mendengarnya seratus kali.</font>

452
00:30:51,069 --> 00:30:52,969
<font color="yellow">Dan untuk wanita, kau harus
memberitahu mereka...</font>

453
00:30:52,969 --> 00:30:54,799
<font color="yellow">...kalau mereka cantik
kapan pun kau bisa.</font>

454
00:31:02,710 --> 00:31:06,450
<font color="yellow">Ada apa?
Kau kesal dengan sesuatu?</font>

455
00:31:06,750 --> 00:31:10,790
<font color="yellow">Kapan Ayah dan Ibu
akan pulang dari jalan-jalan mereka?</font>

456
00:31:11,489 --> 00:31:13,149
<font color="yellow">Mereka bahkan tidak bisa dihubungi.</font>

457
00:31:13,819 --> 00:31:15,419
<font color="yellow">Mereka juga tidak meneleponku.</font>

458
00:31:18,089 --> 00:31:19,129
<font color="yellow">Benar juga.</font>

459
00:31:20,359 --> 00:31:21,899
<font color="yellow">Aku tahu bagaimana perasaanmu sekarang.</font>

460
00:31:25,529 --> 00:31:27,129
<font color="yellow">Mereka akan segera kembali.</font>

461
00:31:27,669 --> 00:31:29,870
<font color="yellow">Aku mengerti bagaimana perasaanmu. Sungguh.</font>

462
00:31:35,009 --> 00:31:36,279
<font color="yellow">(Ratuku)</font>

463
00:31:40,250 --> 00:31:42,020
<font color="yellow">(Ratuku)</font>

464
00:31:42,480 --> 00:31:44,489
<font color="yellow">Dia mengabaikan teleponku berhari-hari.</font>

465
00:31:45,089 --> 00:31:46,419
<font color="yellow">Dia bahkan belum membalas SMS-ku.</font>

466
00:31:46,790 --> 00:31:47,960
<font color="yellow">(Ayah)</font>

467
00:31:47,989 --> 00:31:49,989
<font color="yellow">Oh, Ayah!</font>

468
00:31:52,960 --> 00:31:54,930
<font color="yellow">Ayah, sekarang ada di mana?</font>

469
00:31:55,529 --> 00:31:57,160
<font color="yellow">Di rumah? Baiklah.</font>

470
00:31:58,230 --> 00:32:00,770
<font color="yellow">Paman Young Cheol,
Ayah sekarang ada di rumah.</font>

471
00:32:00,770 --> 00:32:01,839
<font color="yellow">Ayo kita pergi!</font>

472
00:32:01,839 --> 00:32:02,870
<font color="yellow">Apa?</font>

473
00:32:03,739 --> 00:32:04,770
<font color="yellow">Ya.</font>

474
00:32:12,779 --> 00:32:14,080
<font color="yellow">Ayah.</font>

475
00:32:14,080 --> 00:32:16,180
<font color="yellow">Ah, Yool. Sudah datang, Nak.</font>

476
00:32:16,520 --> 00:32:18,790
<font color="yellow">Harusnya jangan bolos kelas.</font>

477
00:32:18,790 --> 00:32:20,520
<font color="yellow">Aku benci Ayah dan Ibu.</font>

478
00:32:20,919 --> 00:32:22,819
<font color="yellow">Kalian berdua jalan-jalan
tanpa memberitahuku...,</font>

479
00:32:22,890 --> 00:32:25,660
<font color="yellow">...dan Ayah bahkan
tidak meneleponku.</font>

480
00:32:26,629 --> 00:32:29,259
<font color="yellow">Ayah tahu betapa aku merindukan Ayah?</font>

481
00:32:33,529 --> 00:32:34,640
<font color="yellow">Maafkan Ayah.</font>

482
00:32:36,799 --> 00:32:38,839
<font color="yellow">Tapi, Ibu masih tidur?</font>

483
00:32:39,270 --> 00:32:42,180
<font color="yellow">Aku sudah di sini. Ibu.</font>

484
00:32:42,980 --> 00:32:46,279
<font color="yellow">Yool, Ibu merasa agak sakit.</font>

485
00:32:46,549 --> 00:32:49,379
<font color="yellow">Ibu sakit?
Di bagian mana?</font>

486
00:32:53,649 --> 00:32:55,890
<font color="yellow">Ayah, kenapa dengan wajah Ayah?</font>

487
00:32:56,020 --> 00:32:57,890
<font color="yellow">Oh, Ayah sedikit terluka.</font>

488
00:32:59,489 --> 00:33:01,029
<font color="yellow">Kusuruh taruh salep di lukamu itu.</font>

489
00:33:01,029 --> 00:33:02,529
<font color="yellow">Aku kelupaan.</font>

490
00:33:08,169 --> 00:33:09,370
<font color="yellow">Dia baik-baik saja?</font>

491
00:33:10,500 --> 00:33:12,069
<font color="yellow">Ya, baguslah.</font>

492
00:33:12,939 --> 00:33:13,939
<font color="yellow">Choi Yool!</font>

493
00:33:15,009 --> 00:33:16,210
<font color="yellow">Kau harus kembali ke sekolah!</font>

494
00:33:17,210 --> 00:33:20,620
<font color="yellow">Aku ingin bersama Ibu sampai dia baikan.</font>

495
00:33:21,850 --> 00:33:25,089
<font color="yellow">Yool, kalau kau bolos kelas,
ibumu akan marah.</font>

496
00:33:25,620 --> 00:33:27,719
<font color="yellow">- Ayo.
- Sebentar.</font>

497
00:33:28,790 --> 00:33:31,859
<font color="yellow">Ibu, aku akan segera kembali.
Aku cinta dengan Ibu!</font>

498
00:33:33,589 --> 00:33:37,399
<font color="yellow">Yool, jangan beri tahu
siapapun kalau ibu sedang sakit.</font>

499
00:33:37,399 --> 00:33:39,799
<font color="yellow">Mereka nanti akan khawatir.
Mengerti?</font>

500
00:33:39,799 --> 00:33:40,799
<font color="yellow">Ya.</font>

501
00:33:41,100 --> 00:33:43,169
<font color="yellow">- Bagus.
- Ayo.</font>

502
00:34:03,060 --> 00:34:04,259
<font color="yellow">Borg Mom.</font>

503
00:34:05,129 --> 00:34:07,560
<font color="yellow">Inikah cinta yang
kurasakan padamu?</font>

504
00:34:49,640 --> 00:34:50,710
<font color="yellow">Borg Mom.</font>

505
00:34:58,279 --> 00:35:01,149
<font color="yellow">Hasil analisisku menunjukkan
kalau kau sedang jatuh cinta.</font>

506
00:35:17,200 --> 00:35:20,100
<font color="yellow">Ya, inilah jawaban
atas pertanyaanku.</font>

507
00:35:21,469 --> 00:35:24,239
<font color="yellow">Aku hanya bisa memercayai suara ini
dan mengikuti kata hatiku, Choi Go Bong.</font>

508
00:35:29,009 --> 00:35:31,710
<font color="yellow">Sekarang jam 3:25 pagi.</font>

509
00:35:32,680 --> 00:35:34,580
<font color="yellow">Tempat makananku
perlu dikosongkan...,</font>

510
00:35:34,719 --> 00:35:36,520
<font color="yellow">...dan rambutku juga perlu dicuci.</font>

511
00:35:36,980 --> 00:35:38,450
<font color="yellow">Ini bisa menyebabkan
kesalahan sistem.</font>

512
00:35:39,120 --> 00:35:42,489
<font color="yellow">Dia berada di klub
sejam yang lalu. Sekarang dia di mana?</font>

513
00:35:44,359 --> 00:35:46,460
<font color="yellow">Mode pelacakan lokasi diaktifkan.</font>

514
00:35:47,700 --> 00:35:49,830
<font color="yellow">(Lokasi Choi Go Bong sekarang ini)</font>

515
00:35:50,299 --> 00:35:51,330
<font color="yellow">Hotel?</font>

516
00:36:02,210 --> 00:36:04,950
<font color="yellow">Menurut sistem pelacakan lokasi,
dia berada di Kamar 1111.</font>

517
00:36:05,009 --> 00:36:07,219
<font color="yellow">Ini sudah dua jam,
tapi dia belum keluar.</font>

518
00:36:07,219 --> 00:36:10,950
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana aku bisa masuk
ke kamar tanpa kunci? Bagian pelayanan.</font>

519
00:36:11,649 --> 00:36:14,189
<font color="yellow">(Panggilan masuk dari Kamar 1111)</font>

520
00:36:16,219 --> 00:36:18,230
<font color="yellow">Terima kasih telah menelepon.
Di sini bagian pelayanan.</font>

521
00:36:20,330 --> 00:36:22,160
<font color="yellow">Aku ingin memesan layanan kamar.</font>

522
00:36:24,529 --> 00:36:25,969
<font color="yellow">Ini layanan kamar.</font>

523
00:36:27,469 --> 00:36:28,799
<font color="yellow">Siapa yang pesan?</font>

524
00:36:35,910 --> 00:36:37,080
<font color="yellow">Ayahnya Yool.</font>

525
00:36:41,350 --> 00:36:45,250
<font color="yellow">(Noda lipstik)</font>

526
00:36:45,250 --> 00:36:46,649
<font color="yellow">(Pakaiannya terlihat berbeda.)</font>

527
00:36:50,319 --> 00:36:51,430
<font color="yellow">Tidak mungkin.</font>

528
00:36:52,589 --> 00:36:55,160
<font color="yellow">Ini gila.
Ini benar-benar gila!</font>

529
00:36:56,129 --> 00:36:58,430
<font color="yellow">Tolong kosongkan tempat makananku...</font>

530
00:37:01,540 --> 00:37:03,739
<font color="yellow">Oh, Ayahnya Yool.</font>

531
00:37:04,040 --> 00:37:05,710
<font color="yellow">Tolong cucikan rambutku untukku.</font>

532
00:37:12,649 --> 00:37:15,120
<font color="yellow">Modus pelacakan ulang GPS diaktifkan.</font>

533
00:37:15,250 --> 00:37:17,290
<font color="yellow">Mode rute tercepat diaktifkan.</font>

534
00:37:38,810 --> 00:37:39,939
<font color="yellow">Ayahnya Yool.</font>

535
00:37:45,250 --> 00:37:47,180
<font color="yellow">30 menit sebelum Yool
harus pergi ke sekolah.</font>

536
00:37:47,279 --> 00:37:49,580
<font color="yellow">Aku akan menemuinya lagi
setelah mengantar Yool.</font>

